{"tid":1723584,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"（分流）中大人可以編好更表，有效率咁分批返屋企補血，再返學校。","createTime":"2019-11-15T08:34:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-15T09:00:58.000Z","uid":161430,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"2eacdec250f6d309eb7fbef54abbdb7d9d327d0d","tid":1723584,"uid":161430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T08:34:56.000Z","msg":"有人話唔想徹離，<br />\n有人想徹離，應該棄守校園，轉返流水式抗爭。<br />\n<br />\n咁咪拎中間位，全世界做分批，例如一三五部分人返屋企抖，另一部分人留守，之後輪更到留守既人二四六返屋企。突發情況除外。<br />\n<br />\n咁咪唔棄守又唔會守到想死，就算警狗都會返狗宿訓，都有輪更啦。<br />\n<br />\n麻煩自己編隊同更表喇。"},{"pid":"8e3ec656274f44632866a9bf53b7cb34e31d522a","tid":1723584,"uid":147916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T08:37:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/67rehV1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F67rehV1.jpg&h=1f4d5a27&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"efefef22c41fc67e2b2df784fb61c4c9712b2ff2","tid":1723584,"uid":161430,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T08:37:21.000Z","msg":"想長期戰鬥就應該做呢樣，而唔係對家都有返屋企訓靚床食好野，睇住你自己消耗時，你就自己24小時死守，訓又訓唔好，脾氣又差，根本似比佢玩。"},{"pid":"d8bd5a9bd418d3f82ef5bef29b67d29656e26a73","tid":1723584,"uid":69595,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T08:38:59.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d0aabdcbb7925d753055548fc7bce5de485743ca","tid":1723584,"uid":291203,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T08:40:04.000Z","msg":"想建議留守ge手足洗地/清潔（要做足放護措施）<br />\n<br />\n唔知有無人做緊？"},{"pid":"b1ed11290343e51979252ed53f03213acb49a349","tid":1723584,"uid":161430,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"d0aabdcbb7925d753055548fc7bce5de485743ca","tid":1723584,"uid":291203,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T08:40:04.000Z","msg":"想建議留守ge手足洗地/清潔（要做足放護措施）<br />\n<br />\n唔知有無人做緊？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T08:42:22.000Z","msg":"推 都重要"},{"pid":"9529aeb06df14db3d6c3ee7f375597c96bbad9ea","tid":1723584,"uid":161430,"like":1,